[[File:PE-mapa-Vertentes.png|thumb|right|250px|Vertentes in [[Pernambuco]].]] '''Vertentes''' is a municipality/city in the state of [[Pernambuco]] in [[Brazil]]. The population in 2009, according with [[Brazilian Institute of Geography and Statistics|IBGE]] was 18.186 inhabitants and the total area is 191.09&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup>.
==Geography==
* State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Agreste]] of Pernambuco * Boundaries - [[Paraiba]] state ('''N'''); [[Caruaru]] and [[Toritama]] ('''S'''); [[Frei Miguelinho]] and [[Santa Maria do Cambucá]] ('''E'''); [[Taquaritinga do Norte]] ('''W'''). * Area - 191.09&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> * Elevation - 401 m * Hidrography - [[Capibaribe River]] * Vegetation - [[Caatinga]] [[hipoxerófila]] * Clima - [[Semi arid]] hot * Annual average temperature - 23.7 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 151&nbsp;km
==Economy==
The main economic activities in '''Vertentes''' are related with [[mineral extraction]] industry and [[agribusiness]], especially creations of [[cattle]], [[goats]], [[sheep]] and [[chickens]].
